WEBVTT

00:00:07.123 --> 00:00:15.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This world would like to make me lonely,
but I got my friends with me.

00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:26.376 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’re trying hard to help
others find friends eternally.

00:00:28.078 --> 00:00:35.251 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I would worry about me,
oh, this world would bring me down.

00:00:38.555 --> 00:00:45.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m feeling better
lifting others off the ground.

00:00:45.395 --> 00:00:50.533 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Look what I’ve found.

00:00:50.533 --> 00:00:57.741 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I want to know what I can do;
I want to give what I can give.

00:00:57.741 --> 00:01:01.111 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That is the best feeling ever.

00:01:01.111 --> 00:01:08.718 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I know this’ll last forever.
I’m where I want to be.

00:01:08.718 --> 00:01:12.222 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is the best life ever.

00:01:16.226 --> 00:01:25.668 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So many good things yet to be done
with these two hands of mine.

00:01:27.370 --> 00:01:36.679 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ll take some love and build us a bridge—
connects your heart to mine.

